<i> in piles</i> ♪

20:33.048 --> 20:35.307
♪<i> And leave them</i>
<i> to blow in the wind</i> ♪

20:35.401 --> 20:37.142
♪<i> Are very inefficient people.</i> ♪

20:37.237 --> 20:39.219
-That was great.
-I have-I have more.

